@MeasureTwiceMNY @jbrendanfrazier @FranklyFinances @jasonfrieds @Zack_Hubbard1 @TKopelman @behaviorgap @thehannahjmoore When services are bundled in almost any industry there's always a pressure towards unbundling them.

